            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
            <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-8">
                <div class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-sm aspect-[16/10] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden cursor-pointer group"
                    onclick="openLightbox(currentIndex)">
                    <div class="w-full h-full transition-all duration-300 opacity-100 relative" id="main-content-area">
                        <img alt="Main Portfolio Showcase" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
                            id="main-carousel-image"
                            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC6Djd9ErefSidRgZ6Gq1oroHbZCk8mJSFme8X_lDuu6lK96F_96Fyqq_8escOIf6K-NOQ-pNH5u3EzdybYOdCEBVWfaR7FQKEAc-PfHZz_1C35DKoHpvAp4rtRAF_kmgmxpks2c4orNVgTuPKsgtFLrVLJMxny_pREvnhBxMnN_TrBPzSqTGKUiL141ncEYoTbo2Cy7fwluN19nEnISMLBs1vmUzQBxQUC8pW4UcUd8lTK-t16FvSii6opsYHG7M2fiwlcn-Eqr2Q" />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity bg-black/5 pointer-events-none">
                            <div
                                class="bg-white/90 dark:bg-black/90 px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">View</span>
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">zoom_in</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
                    <button
                        class="carousel-thumb-btn active bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-xl hover:brightness-95 transition-all outline-none overflow-hidden"
                        onclick="updateCarousel(0)">
                        <img alt="Thumbnail 1" class="w-full h-24 object-cover" src="/assets/login sso.png" />
                    </button>
                    <button
                        class="carousel-thumb-btn bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-xl hover:brightness-95 transition-all outline-none overflow-hidden"
                        onclick="updateCarousel(1)">
                        <img alt="Thumbnail 2" class="w-full h-24 object-cover" src="/assets/main sso.png" />
                    </button>
                    <button
                        class="carousel-thumb-btn bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark rounded-xl hover:brightness-95 transition-all outline-none overflow-hidden"
                        onclick="updateCarousel(2)">
                        <img alt="Thumbnail 3" class="w-full h-24 object-cover" src="/assets/main expanded sso.png" />
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <aside
                class="lg:col-span-4 flex flex-col border-l border-[#0B130F]/10 dark:border-white/10 pl-0 lg:pl-12 pt-4">
                <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-16" id="text-content">
